
Features

user can sign into the app with their email and password
user can follow each other
user can create posts with photos and /or text
user can comment on posts
user can join groups
user can create posts within groups

Brainstorming

name, email, password
following => users
posts, photos, text
comments
groupName, groupType, members

Table Ideas

Users
    firstName
    lastName
    email
    password

Followers
    user_id
    followed by => user.id

Posts
    user.id
    text
    date

post_photos
    post_id
    url

comment_photos
    comment_id
    url

comments
    post_id
    user_id
    text
    date

groups
    group_id
    text

group_posts
    group_id
    text

group_posts_photo
    group_id
    url

